Notes: Both tracks recorded live at CBGB’s, New York City, May 13, 1989. Cover picture - Dave Rick on the road, 1989.
Promo given away with pre-orders of the Galaxie 500 double DVD. Live tracks recorded 30 March 1990 at Club Lingerie, LA.
Free single available with the limited edition of the book Temperature’s Rising: Galaxie 500 an oral and visual history
